  "dateModified": "2026-03-30",
  "datePublished": "2026-03-30",
  "description": "Anarcho-mutualism's five structural commitments each presuppose conditions that collapse destroys. Anarcho-nihilism's relational ontology presupposes only relations — and relations persist where procedures, symmetry, and consensus do not.",
  "name": "Adaptation Does Not Require a Future",
